    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed rooflights, by reason of design, location and scale, comprise an overbearing, incongruous and discordant form of development which would harm the character and appearance of the application site, adjoining terrace, streetscene of Sandringham Road and wider St Marks Conservation Area of which it forms part. The proposed development fails to meet the requirement&amp;nbsp; meet the requirements of London Plan (2021) policies D4, HC1 and Hackney Local Plan (2020) policies LP1 and LP3 and Hackney&#x27;s Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
